# FlowDesk Product Roadmap

## Overview

The FlowDesk Product Roadmap outlines the planned evolution of the platform. Features are organised into releases based on business priority, development complexity, and user value.

The initial focus is to deliver a stable Minimum Viable Product (MVP) that solves the core needs of service-based businesses. Future releases will expand the platform with advanced features, automation, and intelligent business tools.

---

# Product Vision

Build an all-in-one SaaS platform that enables service-based businesses to manage customers, employees, services, bookings, and business operations from one intuitive dashboard.

